# BetterBox Orientation

Pipeline: **crawl → translate/polish (DB queue) → VieNeu-TTS v3 audio → story reader**.

## Repos

- Root: Python pipeline, Docker, `story_db/`
- Nested: `story_reader/` (Next.js) — separate git repo

## Commands & paths

```bash
viterbox/venv/bin/python scripts/story_pipeline/<script>.py
# DB: postgresql://betterbox:betterbox@127.0.0.1:54329/betterbox_story
cd story_db && docker compose up -d
python story_db/apply_migrations.py
python -m story_db.story_pipeline_db.cli <command>
```

## DB-only text (production default)

- Source of truth: `chapters.*_text_content` columns
- Char map: `stories.metadata.char_map_content` (not legacy txt files)
- Do not add new txt output for normal translate/polish
- Do not pass `--genre` unless debugging — genre is inferred from DB

## Audio defaults

- Engine: VieNeu-TTS v3 (Viterbox = legacy)
- Default voice: `preset_binh_an` → `Bình An`
- Audio is **not** auto-enqueued after polish — enqueue manually

